\[ \begin{aligned} \operatorname{length\_group}_{i} &\sim N \left(\beta_{1j[i]}(\operatorname{area}_{\operatorname{BT}}) + \beta_{2j[i]}(\operatorname{area}_{\operatorname{FM}}), \sigma^2 \right) \\ \left( \begin{array}{c} \begin{aligned} &\beta_{1j} \\ &\beta_{2j} \end{aligned} \end{array} \right) &\sim N \left( \left( \begin{array}{c} \begin{aligned} &\mu_{\beta_{1j}} \\ &\mu_{\beta_{2j}} \end{aligned} \end{array} \right) , \left( \begin{array}{cc} \sigma^2_{\beta_{1j}} & \rho_{\beta_{1j}\beta_{2j}} \\ \rho_{\beta_{2j}\beta_{1j}} & \sigma^2_{\beta_{2j}} \end{array} \right) \right) \text{, for year j = 1,} \dots \text{,J} \end{aligned} \]
